<Layout title="About" description="About A2 Farm Finder, a directory of farms, CSAs, and farmers markets around Washtenaw County.">
  <h1>About A2 Farm Finder</h1>
  <p>
    A2 Farm Finder is an independent directory of farms, CSA programs, and
    farmers markets across Washtenaw County &mdash; including Ann Arbor,
    Chelsea, Dexter, Saline, Manchester, and nearby towns.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our goal is to make it easier to find local food: where to sign up for a
    CSA share, when farmers markets are open, and which farms sell what.
  </p>
  <p>
    Listings are compiled from publicly available information and farm
    websites. Details like pricing, hours, and seasons can change &mdash;
    always check with the farm or market directly before visiting or signing
    up.
  </p>
  <p>
    Know a farm, CSA, or market that should be listed?
    <a href="mailto:hello@a2farmfinder.com">Let us know</a>.
  </p>
</Layout>
